<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.1.2">
<l>ceruvaraimuṉ ṉācaṟutta cilaiyaṉṟō kaittalatta teṉkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>poruvaraimuṉ pōrtolaitta poṉṉāḻi maṟṟorukai yeṉkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>oruvaraiyum niṉṉoppā roppilā veṉṉappā veṉkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>karuvaraipōl niṉṟāṉaik kaṇṇapurat tammāṉaik kaṇṭāḷ kollō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“The bow that once quickly cut down [his] battle foes</l>
<l rend="indent">is in [his] hands, isn’t it,” she declares;</l>
<l>“And in the other hand is the golden discus that once destroyed</l>
<l rend="indent">warriors in battle,” she declares;</l>
<l>“They do not compare anyone to you, my father who is incomparable,”</l>
<l rend="indent">she declares.</l>
<l>Did she see the lord of Kaṇṇapuram, the one who stands like a dark mountain?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
